"{\"uid\": \"bbj.hu-budapest-events-city-hungary-hosting-olympics-would-require-comprehensive-cooperation\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"F\\u00fcrjes said Hungary had demonstrated it was capable of organizing an Olympics like the one that closed in Paris on Sunday by hosting a number of European and world championships over the past 7-8 years.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12, \"end\": 19, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.8029787587394798, \"rank\": 0.1594690305701151, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}, {\"begin\": 106, \"end\": 111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9998747440753185, \"rank\": 0.00012527161568208768, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It would take a huge effort, but the most important thing would be establishing a comprehensive cooperation, and that's why I am a bit skeptical,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 204, \"to\": 361, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"F\\u00fcrjes said the context allowing for \\\"full agreement\\\" between the Hungarian Olympic Committee, the mayor and municipal council of Budapest, the political right and left wings, the government, and the nation as a whole was \\\"not yet apparent.\\\"\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 429, \"end\": 456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungarian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hungarian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungarian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungarian_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 493, \"end\": 501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999999512234593, \"rank\": 4.272927405169341e-08, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He suggested that if the sides could \\\"put aside their differences\\\" on the matter, allowing for the establishment of a consensus, Hungary would have a good chance to make an effort to host the next Olympics in Europe.\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 735, \"end\": 742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.8029787587394798, \"rank\": 0.1594690305701151, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Producing journalism that is worthy of the name is a costly business.\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 893, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For over 30 years, the publishers, editors and reporters of the Budapest Business Journal have striven to bring you business news that works, information that you can trust, that is factual, accurate and presented without fear or favor.Newspaper organizations across the globe have struggled to find a business model that allows them to continue to excel, without compromising their ability to perform.\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 1296, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 958, \"end\": 983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest_Business_Journal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Budapest Business Journal\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest_Business_Journal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest_Business_Journal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most recently, some have experimented with the idea of involving their most important stakeholders, their readers.We would like to offer that same opportunity to our readers.\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1471, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We would like to invite you to help us deliver the quality business journalism you require.\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hit our Support the BBJ button and you can choose the how much and how often you send us your contributions.\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1672, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1584, \"end\": 1587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boeing_Business_Jet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BBJ\", \"types\": [\"Q11436\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boeing_Business_Jet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boeing_Business_Jet\"}]}]}"